author: Chris Wright
title: Arsene Wenger protest makes it to Minnesota United vs. Atlanta United - ESPN FC
text:
Arsene Wenger protest makes it to Minnesota United vs. Atlanta United Some disgruntled Gunners supporters made their feelings known ahead of the UCL clash with Bayern. 
As you're no doubt aware, Arsene Wenger is coming under fire (once again) from certain sections of the Arsenal fanbase. 
Placards and banners were on display both before and after the Gunners' embarrassing 10-2 aggregate mauling by Bayern Munich in the Champions League. 
Indeed, one fan even producing a slightly embarrassing Brexit-themed (Wexit) flag for Saturday's FA Cup tie with Lincoln City.
